{"tid":827541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最緊要正字】國泰神回應 錯體機變「特別版」獲激讚","createTime":"2018-09-19T04:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T05:46:00.000Z","uid":1221,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1bfc795dcded0066b570691ab5d1c3fd8228cce9","tid":827541,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/120654_08f8f875e216618a546a227ae0b25e11.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F120654_08f8f875e216618a546a227ae0b25e11.jpeg&h=aa9ac938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關公災難見唔少，相對地公關手段夠高明就不單可以撥亂反正，還可反過來獲得一片讚好。今日國泰（0293）的公關團隊就給予了一個示範。<br />\n<br />\n話說今早飛機師群組瘋傳一組照片，顯示國泰一架777飛機機身上的國泰英文名字竟然印錯，由原本「CATHAY PACIFIC」，印錯成「CATHAY PACIIC」，另一幅照片亦見到有員工以膠紙遮蓋「IIC」三個字，不過一黃遮三醜有點礙眼。<br />\n<br />\n錯誤固然低級，但國泰公關迅速反應，於Facebook專頁立即以「突發！期間限定777機隊外觀」為題回應，聲稱「特別版向來一瞬即逝。因此她正返回基地重新塗裝。再見！」，幽默的自嘲加上以「特別版」去形容印錯字，既把錯誤輕輕帶過，亦說明了已經立即處理，短短23個字的回應盡顯出色危機處理，難怪網民留言都一致讚賞，甚至有人建議國泰索性將「特別版」飛機出模型作紀念。<br />\n<br />\n至於呢架「特別版」飛機，據了解其實係新機，未正式服役，所以所有乘客都只能緣慳一面，有點可惜啊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/120656_e0566da917c917801030e9719f180976.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F120656_e0566da917c917801030e9719f180976.jpeg&h=62942410&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c56805b6a4d21f5af3b405f4acd96ac5772ed81","tid":827541,"uid":55386,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有點柒"},{"pid":"2cb6c9058117de734865ee98e211706ca3eaa9b5","tid":827541,"uid":155818,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:09:27.000Z","msg":"你唔痴都唔覺<br />\n痴撚左就好覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6045baf004038afa1af97a1c4646e2aff7b4579","tid":827541,"uid":37733,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:11:06.000Z","msg":"其實個回應有幾神？"},{"pid":"9b05260dc0498a1fdff33a3f6049819429d162c5","tid":827541,"uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"另一幅照片亦見到有員工以膠紙遮蓋「IIC」三個字，不過一黃遮三醜有點礙眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba7cc6d3e893b2f84dfb33cf12aa7c8eb1c13c4","tid":827541,"uid":193497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"做公關做得唔好 食得屎啦"},{"pid":"e3b354757a83932de56a0f399db4338e4a960226","tid":827541,"uid":838,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"得啲飛機膠會讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常人真係WFC"},{"pid":"1d1f74207818cb27f829502fd45a6fcc644b14e0","tid":827541,"uid":37941,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:46:51.000Z","msg":"因航不嬲欠F"},{"pid":"24ab907400d2927c86af28ad7f739edc5b479b78","tid":827541,"uid":43964,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/125354_83d30263876bc93bc16493db034786af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F125354_83d30263876bc93bc16493db034786af.png&h=9c26962c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新機？15歲都黎，大過兒登仔<br />\n<br />\nOn99 傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6382b79a1005058b53d9879cbd8ccf594692f66","tid":827541,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"cx最近換咗pr？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425e87b040aa7b823b6af407bf30070fda16e648","tid":827541,"uid":122939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24ab907400d2927c86af2